To plot indicator values, in the OnData event handler, call the Plot method.

private StickSandwich _sticksandwich;

// In Initialize()
var symbol = AddEquity("SPY").Symbol;
_sticksandwich = StickSandwich(symbol);

// In OnData()
if (_sticksandwich.IsReady)
{
    Plot("My Indicators", "sticksandwich", _sticksandwich.Current.Value);
}
